## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `curl "/api/geocode?q=Paris&type=municipality"` to verify filtering.
- `curl "/api/geocode?q=75001&type=municipality"` to verify zip code results.

### Manual Verification
- Open Admin panel, go to Users, click "Configurer" on a Mairie agent.
- Type in the new search box and verify that only communes/cities are suggested.
- Select a suggestion and verify it is added to the list.
